name: zeny

name: job exp

description: Sprout of Yggdrasil, filled with powerful vital energy. Restores 50% HP and 50% SP. Cannot be used in PVP. Required Level: 1

name: change name card
description: A card that allows one to change their name. Use to change your character's name!

name: leaf of yggdrasil
description: Leaf of Yggdrasil, filled with powerful vital energy. Can revive characters who have lost their ability to fight.

name: magical stone
description: There's a rumor that a person who finds a Magical Stone can use it to initialize their stats. Use to reset your Stat Points.

name: neuralizer
description: A stick that emits a blue light when you press the button. Those who see this light will forget parts of their memory. Can be used to reset skill points.

name: gym pass
description: A special membership coupon for the gym. Use to increase your weight limit by 1,000.

name: elemental converter (fire)
description: Once used, your weapon's attribute will change to Fire for a set time. Lasts 20 minutes.

name: elemental converter (water)
description: Once used, your weapon's attribute will change to Water for a set time. Lasts 20 minutes.

name: elemental converter (wind)
description: Once used, your weapon's attribute will change to Wind for a set time. Lasts 20 minutes.

name: elemental converter (earth)
description: Once used, your weapon's attribute will change to Earth for a set time. Lasts 20 minutes.

name: warehouse expansion voucher
description: A certificate issued by Kafra Corporation, provided only to adventurers who have made contributions to the Chamber of Commerce. Use it to increase your Warehouse storage space.

name: endless atk buff
description: Purchase to obtain the Endless Strength Blessing.

name: endless m.atk buff
description: Purchase to obtain the Endless Magic Blessing.

name: endless mspd buff
description: Purchase to obtain the Endless Speed Blessing.

name: endless meditatio buff
description: Purchase to obtain the Endless Meditation Blessing.

name: angeling's blessing
description: Purchase to gain 1 stack of Angeling's Blessing.

name: deviling's curse
description: Purchase to remove 1 stack of Deviling's Curse.

name: kingdom missions
description: The kingdom herald's mysterious quest book. Use to accept mysterious quests.

name: ultimate showdown invitation letter
description: A mysterious invitation from Tony Chir, the Arena Master, which is necessary to participate in the Ultimate Showdown. The handwriting of the invitation is rather messy, making it impossible for anyone to read what is written, but the Arena Master can easily tell whether it is true or fake.

name: a candy box that contains something.
description:
A <color=#FF69B4>sharing box</color> that is filled with Halloween candy.
You will find that it is filled with snacks.
It will be placed on the ground after you use it to share with everyone.
Each person can only take 1 piece of candy. There is a total of 10 pieces of candy.
<color=#FF0000>(The sharing box will expire if you leave it for a long time.)</color>

name: chunky poring candy
description: Chunky Poring Candy exclusive to the Halloween event.\nEating it will make you big and fat, and some stats might get a buff or debuff. You can only eat a maximum of 5! Don't be greedy!\n<color=#FF0000>(The candy will expire if you don't eat it.)</color>

name: deviruchi candy
description: Deviruchi Candy exclusive to the Halloween event.\nEating it will make you small and skinny, and some stats might get a buff or debuff. You can only eat a maximum of 5! Don't be greedy!\n<color=#FF0000>(The candy will expire if you don't eat it.)</color>

name: ghost candy
description: Ghost Candy exclusive to the Halloween event.\nYou will enter Hiding mode after eating it and Crit Rate will increase greatly. The effect cannot be stacked.\n<color=#FF0000>(The candy will expire if you don't eat it.)</color>

name: pumpkin candy
description: Pumpkin Candy exclusive to the Halloween event.\nYou will enter Fervor mode after eating it and you will deal more damage against Large monsters. It has adverse side effects. The effect cannot be stacked.\n<color=#FF0000>(The candy will expire if you don't eat it.)</color>

name: candy
description: Normal candy dropped by monsters in the Halloween event. Jakk will tabulate the number of candies obtained and you will be ranked accordingly.

name: starshot
description: Starshot used during the Christmas Shootout event. Can be fired using the Christmas Elk Slingshot in Geffen to deal moderate damage to Small Monster Balloons.\n<color=#FF0000>[Slingshot can be used at Base Lv.25 and above.]</color>\nConsume Odin's Blessing to earn Starshot.

name: meteor pellets
description: Meteor Pellets used during the Christmas Shootout event. Can be fired using the Christmas Elk Slingshot in Geffen to deals high damage to Medium and Small Monster Balloons.\n<color=#FF0000>[Slingshot can be used at Base Lv.25 and above.]</color>\nYou can obtain Meteor Pellets from Carnival Activity Chests.

name: icicle ammo
description: Icicle Ammo used during the Christmas Shootout event. Can be fired using the Christmas Elk Slingshot in Geffen to deal extreme damage to Medium and Large Monster Balloons.\n<color=#FF0000>[Slingshot can be used at Base Lv.25 and above.]</color>\nYou can obtain Icicle Ammo after clearing instances in the Heart Pedestal.

name: cannon ball
description: Cannon Balls used during the Christmas Shooting Festival. Can be fired using the fort in Geffen.\nGrants you a chance to earn extra rewards when shooting Gold Angeling Balloons, and has a <color=#FF0000>0.05%</color> chance to launch one-hit critical shots.\n<color=#FF0000>[The fort can be used at Base Lv.25 and above]</color>

name: fireworks
description: Firecrackers used in the Nian's Attack event. It deals a small amount of damage and can be equipped on the Quick Use bar.\nSpecial Effect: Hit Nian to decrease its <color=#FF0000>armor</color> by 10%.

name: firecrackers
description: Firecrackers used in the Nian's Attack event. It deals a small amount of damage and can be equipped on the Quick Use bar.\nSpecial Effect: Once Nian's armor is broken, Firecrackers will deal a <color=#FF0000>large amount of damage</color> to it.

name: spring festival dumplings
description: Delicious dumplings with eastern characteristics made especially for the Spring Festival.\nSTR +10, VIT +10, and DEX +10 for 40 minutes.

name: spring festival rice cakes
description: Delicious rice cakes with eastern characteristics made especially for the Spring Festival.\nAGI +10, INT+10, and LUK +10 for 40 minutes.

name: new year gift box
description: Exclusive New Year Gift Box. Open to randomly obtain 8888/88888/888888 Zeny, and a random Spring Festival event item (Fireworks/Firecrackers/New Year Dish/Lucky Bag).

name: lucky trove
description: Lucky Trove. Open to randomly obtain a random Equipment Upgrading Metal, Refining Material, or Enchantment Material.\nThere is also a small chance to obtain Spring Festival exclusive Mount: Lion's Head Fireworks. (Non-bound item.)

name: lantern festival gift box
description: A Lantern Festival Gift Box exclusive for Kafra VIPs.\nGet after successfully uniting the lanterns.

name: golden rabbit sweet dumplings
description:
Eating it will grant you the Golden Rabbit Sweet Dumplings Blessing.
Legend has it that if you go near someone who has eaten Silver Rabbit Sweet Dumplings, a bond will form between the both of you. When both of you perform the designated action within a short time span, you will receive Jade Rabbit's Blessing for 12 hours.
The designated action changes every day. Try asking around to find out what it is!
<color=#FF0000>(The dumplings will expire if you don't eat it.)</color>

name: silver rabbit sweet dumplings
description:
Eating it will grant you the Silver Rabbit Sweet Dumplings Blessing.
Legend has it that if you go near someone who has eaten Golden Rabbit Sweet Dumplings, a bond will form between the both of you. When both of you perform the designated action within a short time span, you will receive Jade Rabbit's Blessing for 12 hours.
The designated action changes every day. Try asking around to found out what it is!
<color=#FF0000>(The dumplings will expire if you don't eat it.)</color>

name: eden guerilla forces supplies
description: Eden Guerilla Forces Supplies. Open to randomly obtain a Equipment Upgrading Metal, Refining Material, and Enchantment Material.\nThere is also a small chance to obtain Candy Battle Exclusive Mount <Honey Jar> (Non-bound item).

name: christmas premium pack
description: Christmas Premium Pack. Open to randomly obtain a Equipment Upgrading Metal, Refining Material, Enchantment Material, and Limited-time bound mount.\nThere is also a small chance to obtain Christmas Exclusive Mount<Sasquatch Sled> (Non-bound item).

name: 太妃糖弹丸
description: 蜜糖大作战中使用的太妃糖弹丸，可在乐园团中使用糖果弹弓进行发射，对工蜂可造成不错的威力， 消耗奥丁或参与MVP击杀可获得太妃糖弹丸\n<color=#FF0000>【BaseLv25以上可以使用弹弓】</color>

name: 棉花糖弹丸
description: 蜜糖大作战中使用的棉花糖弹丸，可在乐园团中使用糖果弹弓进行发射，对公主蜂可造成不错的威力， 参与日常副本或参与MVP击杀可获得棉花糖弹丸\n<color=#FF0000>【BaseLv25以上可以使用弹弓】</color>

name: 棒棒糖弹丸
description: 在乐园团中仅可使用糖果炮台进行发射\n命中黄金蜂后女王时有概率掉落额外奖励，并有0.1%几率直接击落的超级暴击效果，在儿童节商人处购买或参与MVP击杀获得可获得棒棒糖弹丸\n<color=#FF0000>【BaseLv25以上可以使用炮台】</color>

name: 击退飞拳
description: 击退飞拳

name: 定身
description: 定身

name: 隐身药水
description: 隐身药水

name: 召唤雪人兄弟
description: 召唤雪人兄弟

name: 瓦斯毒气
description: 瓦斯毒气

name: 星空葡萄
description: CoCo星空系列饮品。\n全属性+5，持续20分钟。

name: nightmare mark
description: A Nightmare Mark is necessary for entering Nightmare Mode instances.

name: magic box key
description: Item used to open Magic Box chests.

name: resurrection scroll
description: Item for resurrecting in place in a Heart Pedestal instance. When used in Nightmare, it grants exemption to resurrection penalties.

name: soul gemstone
description: Using skills that cost Blue Gemstones in Nightmare Mode also requires the use of Soul Gemstones. Does not reduce card effects.

name: soul contract
description: For use in Nightmare Mode's Soul Buyback. Speeds up the buyback process of an equipment slot.

name: command flag
description: A mysterious flag possessing the power of Nightmare. After planting it into the ground, 5 party members can active the mysterious magic circle by standing in the required position. When all the magic circles are activated, the party members can obtain any buff among <color=#ff3300>damage</color>, <color=#33ccff>defense</color>, and <color=#009900>recovery</color>, which lasts for 5 minutes.\n<color=#FF0000>Only can be used in Nightmare Instance, and the buff will disabled when the player leaves the instance. Please do not use it in narrow places to avoid not activating the magic circle.</color>

name: nightmare leaf of yggdrasil
description: Exclusive item for Nightmare mode. Leaf of Yggdrasil, filled with powerful vital energy. Can resurrect characters who have lost their ability to fight. <color=#FF0000>Can only be used in Nightmare instance. Disabled in other scenes.</color>

name: salt-baked crab pot i
description: Delicious crab casserole with a savory aroma infused with the ocean’s freshness.\nHoly Attribute Enhancement +10% for 30 minutes.

name: sea bream skewer i
description: A simple fish steak is the ultimate test of a cook's mastery of flame grilling.\nGhost Attribute Enhancement +10% for 30 minutes.

name: adventurer's salad
description: A common dish made from fresh and delicious ingredients. Eaten by Adventurers all over the continent.\nAll Stats +3 for 10 minutes.

name: birthday cake
description: A small Birthday Cake, shared with all Guild members!\nHP +5%, P.ATK +5%, M.ATK +5%, Final DEF +5%, and Final M.DEF +5% for 12 hours.

name: 芋圆烧仙草
description: 夏季的消暑饮品，芋圆烧仙草。\nPVP负面状态减免+10%，\nPVP负面状态抵抗+10%，持续1小时。

name: 冰镇西瓜汁
description: 夏季的消暑饮品，冰镇西瓜汁。\n物理攻击+10%，\n魔法攻击+10%，持续1小时。

name: 芒果冰沙
description: 夏季的消暑饮品，芒果冰沙。\nPVP最终物伤附加+10%，\nPVP最终魔伤附加+10%，持续1小时。

name: dried fruit platter i
description: A platter of dried fruits and nuts.\nNeutral Attribute Enhancement +10% for 30 minutes.

name: snowy milk cake i
description: Frozen milk cake with an unforgettable taste and texture.\nFire Attribute Enhancement +10%, Earth Attribute Enhancement +10% for 30 minutes.

name: crispy chili herb i
description: A spicy vegetable dish that’s delectably crispy.\nWind Attribute Enhancement +10%, Water Attribute Enhancement +10% for 30 minutes.

name: witchy fish fillet i
description: Fresh fish fillet flavored with a special blend of spices. A popular dish among witches looking for something a little different.\nPoison Attribute Enhancement +10% for 30 minutes.

name: 端午抽奖券
description: 端午粽情好礼活动，棋盘游戏投掷骰子的消耗道具。嘉年华活跃度奖励。活动结束后会被销毁，并返还一部分冒险家色拉。

name: 蒲酒升平系列发型
description: Unlock the male \"青箬\" or female \"芳兰\" hairstyle after use.

name: new super star frame
description: A well-designed unlocking tool. Unlocks the [New Super Star] frame after use.

name: pet change name card
description: A card with a mystical power. Used to change a pet's nickname.

name: pet frisbee
description: It's said that if you use all your strength, it can fly very far. Use to increase a pet's Favor by 100.

name: summer festival haste voucher
description: A mysterious voucher that contains time powder. Use it to speed up Summer Festival events by 3 hours.

name: nosiege runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Attack Resonance</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nIncreases your Final Physical Damage Bonus, Final Magic Damage Bonus, Final PVP Physical Damage Bonus, and Final PVP Magic Damage Bonus by <color=#CA2E0AFF>5%*number of party members under the same effect</color>.

name: rhydo runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Defense Resonance</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nIncreases your Final Physical Damage Reduction, Final Magic Damage Reduction, Final PVP Physical Damage Reduction, and Final PVP Magic Damage Reduction by <color=#CA2E0AFF>5%*number of party members under the same effect</color>.

name: verkana runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Shield Resonance</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nGrants yourself a shield equal to <color=#CA2E0AFF>10% of Max HP*number of party members under the same effect</color>.

name: isia runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Skill Link</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nWhen a party member under the same effect casts an active skill, all members recover 1% of their HP.

name: asir runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Crit Link</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nWhen a party member under the same effect triggers a critical hit, all members recover 0.15% of their HP.

name: urj runestone
description: After using this item, it carries <color=#CA2E0AFF>Life Chain</color> status for 2 minutes, with a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nIf you take damage with this status, damage taken is reduced by <color=#CA2E0AFF>3%*no. of people in your team with this status</color>, and the remaining damage is shared equally by all team members with this status within a 30-meter radius.

name: turisus runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Movement Speed Burst</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nIncreases Movement Speed of all party members by <color=#CA2E0AFF>0.5*number of party members under the same effect</color>.

name: pertz runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Effect Burst</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nWhile under the effect, inflicting a debuff on the enemy allows you to ignore <color=#CA2E0AFF>5%*number of party members under the same effect</color> of the enemy's Effect Resistance, Debuff Resistance, and PVP Debuff Resistance.

name: hagalas runestone
description: Use it to grant the <color=#CA2E0AFF>Stun Burst</color> effect for 2 minutes. Has a cooldown of 5 minutes.\nEach time you lose 10% of your HP, there is a <color=#CA2E0AFF>5%*number of party members under the same effect</color> chance of stunning enemies within 2 meters of you for 1 second.

name: pet gacha scroll
description: Pet Adventure exchange item. Can be exchanged for rewards at the Prontera Pet Exchange Merchant. Destroyed at the end of the event, and returned to Adventurer's in part as Salad.

name: magic gear fuel
description: Used to power the Magic Gear.

name: 周年演唱会邀请函
description: 10月15日将举行周年演唱会，届时可在游戏内收看直播。使用该邀请函，可以提交祝福语，有机会在演唱会现场展示哦~首次提交祝福语会得到神秘礼品。活动结束后，该道具会销毁。

name: vote for the chosen lv.1
description: Used to vote for parties in the War of the Chosen, which can give the party 1 additional voting points. The item will be destroyed after the voting phase is over, so please use it in time.

name: vote for the chosen lv.2
description: Used to vote for parties in the War of the Chosen, which can give the party 3 additional voting points. The item will be destroyed after the voting phase is over, so please use it in time.

name: vote for the chosen lv.3
description: Used to vote for parties in the War of the Chosen, which can give the party 10 additional voting points. The item will be destroyed after the voting phase is over, so please use it in time.

name: vote for the chosen lv.4
description: Used to vote for parties in the War of the Chosen, which can give the party 20 additional voting points. The item will be destroyed after the voting phase is over, so please use it in time.

name: half-year anniversary gacha scroll
description: Item used for the 2022 New Year lottery. The more scrolls you collect before the lottery starts, the higher the probability of winning the grand prize. All the Gacha Scrolls will be destroyed after the event is over.

name: party creation voucher
description: A voucher used to create a party in War of the Chosen, a symbol of power. The item will be destroyed after the preparation phase is over, so please use it in time.

name: 加农炮丸
description: 圣诞射击大作战中使用的加农炮丸，在吉芬中仅可使用炮台进行发射\n命中黄金天使波利气球时有概率掉落额外奖励，并具有<color=#FF0000>0.05%</color>概率直接击破的超级暴击效果\n<color=#FF0000>【BaseLv25以上可以使用炮台】</color>

name: 星星弹珠
description: 圣诞射击大作战中使用的星星弹珠，可在吉芬中使用麋鹿弹弓进行发射，对小型的魔物气球可造成不错的威力\n<color=#FF0000>【BaseLv25以上可以使用弹弓】</color> \n 消耗奥丁时获得星星弹珠

name: 陨石弹珠
description: 圣诞射击大作战中使用的陨石弹珠，可在吉芬中使用麋鹿弹弓进行发射，对中小型的魔物气球的威力十足\n<color=#FF0000>【BaseLv25以上可以使用弹弓】</color> \n嘉年华活跃度宝箱获得陨石弹珠

name: 冰锥弹珠
description: 圣诞射击大作战中使用的冰锥弹珠，可在吉芬中使用麋鹿弹弓进行发射，对中大型的魔物气球造成的威力巨大\n<color=#FF0000>【BaseLv25以上可以使用弹弓】 </color> 心之座通关后获得冰锥弹珠

name: eddga’s knuckle
description: An item used in the Lunar Year of the Tiger event. After using it, players can summon Eddga, who will charge power for 10 seconds, and after 10 seconds, it will deal huge damage to the Nian according to the number of players around itself. The damage will be credited to the item user.

name: doritos超浓芝士味
description: Doritos超浓芝士味薯片。\n享用后采矿时间缩短 10%，持续20分钟。

name: doritos烧烤味
description: Doritos烧烤味薯片。\n享用后捕捉宠物成功率 +5%，持续20分钟。

name: doritos原味
description: Doritos原味薯片。\n享用后非战斗状态下移动速度 +1，持续20分钟。

name: tome of travers
description: A textbook written by Travers, a Class Conversion instructor, with bad handwriting but worth reading. Can be used to activate branches of Class Conversion.

name: true love wedding voucher
description: Freyja's Wedding Planners' special gift. Use it to get a 50% discount on a custom wedding.\n<color=#FF0000>[Will be taken back after the event ends]</color>

name: clear water
description: Absolutely clean water. It has the meaning of blessing when it is poured on others.

name: lifebuoy
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Lifebuoy” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: super water balloon
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Super Water Balloon” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: pressure boost valve
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Pressure Boost Valve” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: water balloon
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Water Balloon” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: energy drink
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Energy Drink” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: kafra's trial card (1 day)
description: The Trial Card is Kafra Corporation's way of providing adventurers with even more rewards! Activate to enjoy Kafra's Trial Card for 1 day. You can choose 7 privileges when you activate the Trial Card (cannot used with VIP Card).

name: 3× exp card
description: Use to increase Odin idle EXP gain to 3 times for 12 hours, sharing the same 20-hour cooldown with the 5x card.

name: 5× exp card
description: Use to increase Odin idle EXP gain to 5 times for 12 hours, sharing the same 20-hour cooldown with the 3x card.

name: 工程师003的加班宵夜
description:
工程师003加班时候常吃的宵夜，吃完以后感觉加班都更有活力了。
效果：
最大HP、物理攻击、魔法攻击、最终魔防效果、最终物防效果提高+3%
时效：30分钟

name: lifebuoy
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Lifebuoy” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: super water balloon
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Super Water Balloon” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: pressure boost valve
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Pressure Boost Valve” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: water balloon
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Water Balloon” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: energy drink
description: Item used in the Songkran Festival event. Consume it to get a chance to use the “Energy Drink” in the Water Gun Battle. Players using it outside the event will perform the action [Throw Water].

name: 梦幻炖鱼ⅰ
description: 加入各种菌类的炖鱼，色泽和味道都很梦幻，食用后对火属性魔物伤害增加8%，受火属性魔物伤害减少8%，持续30分钟。

name: 海胆焗饭ⅰ
description: 铺满海胆黄的喷香料理，入口咸鲜带甜，食用后对水属性魔物伤害增加8%，受水属性魔物伤害减少8%，持续30分钟。

name: 返魂骨汤ⅰ
description: 能让死者流口水的鱼汤，最挑食的人也会赞不绝口，食用后对风属性魔物伤害增加8%，受风属性魔物伤害减少8%，持续30分钟。

name: 烧汁鳝段ⅰ
description: 细煮慢炖的家常菜，十分注重汤汁的调味与食材的选取，食用后对地属性魔物伤害增加8%，受地属性魔物伤害减少8%，持续30分钟。

name: 白灼螺片ⅰ
description: 在开水中烫至螺肉卷边后蘸酱食用，味道爽脆可口，食用后对毒属性魔物伤害增加8%，受毒属性魔物伤害减少8%，持续30分钟。

name: 龟壳烧肉ⅰ
description: 以龟壳为容器的特色菜，十分下饭，食用后对不死属性魔物伤害增加8%，受不死属性魔物伤害减少8%，持续30分钟。

name: candy gift
description: A candy basket filled with candy in various colors is a good gift for your favored companion. Charm +20, Favor +10. When given after married, you gain 2 Couple EXP.

name: roller coaster cheese chips
description: The young potato hero keeps fighting and levelling up in a boundless world of cheese - until he evolves into Roller Coaster Cheese Chips and launches himself into your mouth contentedly. 4）未经确认单独使用消耗掉道具，将不会获得补偿；

description: 从破损的古老盔甲上取下，上面有诡异的花纹。

name: 变异骨刺
description: 苍白泛黄的骨刺，需小心边缘的锯齿。

name: 异能结晶
description: 蕴含神秘力量的结晶。

name: 诡异树枝
description: 干枯扭曲的树枝，很适合通灵。

name: 锋利叶片
description: 修长的锋利叶片，边缘带有细小锯齿。

name: 幽魂碎屑
description: 散发淡淡荧光的结晶碎屑。

name: 彩色鳞片
description: 美丽的鳞片，在阳光下能折射七彩的光。

name: 光滑鬃毛
description: 柔软的亮色鬃毛，十分顺滑。

name: 魔法布料
description: 神奇的魔法布料，被裁剪时会呼救。

name: 染血獠牙
description: 撕裂过无数敌人的獠牙，锋锐无比。

name: 剧毒指甲
description: 已上毒的指甲，千万不要被它抓伤。

name: 荆棘化石
description: 古老的石板，上面有荆棘状花纹。

name: 鲜血精华
description: 鲜红的结晶体，据说某种魔物很喜欢。

name: 寄生苔藓
description: 附着在石头上的大块苔藓，生命力极强。

name: 炽热铁块
description: 烧红的金属块，隐隐可见黑色的碳化斑点。

name: 粗壮树根
description: 粗壮的植物根茎，带有细小的根须。

name: 漆黑火药
description: 危险的黑色混合物，请谨慎使用。

name: 粘稠体液
description: 粘稠的生物体液，几乎不怎么流动。

name: 优质黏土
description: 含砂粒很少、黏性极强的土壤。

name: 琥珀碎片
description: 透明的琥珀碎片，里面的小生物已不知去向。

name: 浑浊体液
description: 料理材料，粘稠且浑浊的怪物体液

name: 角质细粉
description: 料理材料，老化的怪物表皮研磨成的粉末

name: 异化组织
description: 料理材料，变异的细胞组织，仿佛在不断分裂生长

name: 活体树叶
description: 料理材料，会自己移动寻找生长场所的树叶

name: 硬皮果实
description: 料理材料，果皮十分坚硬，但内部的果肉却柔软多汁

name: 新生枝芽
description: 料理材料，充满生命力的植物嫩芽

name: tome of twilight fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Twilight. Use a Tome of Twilight to select one card from the following: Eclipse Series Card, Dragon Fly Series Card, Mastering Series Card, or Ghostring Series Card.

name: tome of glory fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Glory. Use a Tome of Glory to select one card from the following: King Dramoh Series Card, Toad Series Card, Deviling Series Card, or Angeling Series Card.

name: tome of fate fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Fate. Use a Tome of Fate to select one card from the following: Mistress Series Card, Phreeoni Series Card, Kraken Series Card, or Eddga Series Card.

name: tome of eternity fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Eternity. Use a Tome of Eternity to select one card from the following: Maya Series Card, Orc Hero Series Card, Pharaoh Series Card, or Orc Lord Series Card.

name: tome of origin fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Origin. Use a Tome of Origin to select one card from the following: Golden Thief Bug Series Card, Drake Series Card, or Osiris Series Card.

name: tome of absolution fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Absolution. Use a Tome of Absolution to select one card from the following: Strouf Series Card, Moonlight Flower Series Card, or Dracula Series Card.

name: tome of sages fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Sages. Use a Tome of Sages to select one card from the following: Doppelganger Series Card, Amon Ra Series Card, Dark Priest Series Card, Vagabond Wolf Series Card, or Dark Lord Series Card.

name: ancient tome fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of the Ancient. Use a Tome of the Ancient to select one from the following cards: Timekeeper Series Card, Morroc Series Card, Owl Duke Series Card, Chimera Series Card, or Mysteltainn Series Card.

name: tome of shade fragment
description: A valuable fragment. Collect 360 of them to redeem a Tome of Shade. Use a Tome of Shade to select one card from the following: Tao Gunka Series Card, Lost Dragon Series Card, Ogretooth Series Card, Necromancer Series Card, or Mutant Dragonoid Series Card.

name: 亡魂之书碎片
description: 珍贵的碎片，集齐360个碎片可以兑换一本亡魂之书。使用亡魂之书，可从下列卡片中选择一张获得：死灵骑士系列卡片、堕落的大神官希巴姆系列卡片、纳户特基格系列卡片、腔棘鱼系列卡片、贝雷杰系列卡片

name: crucian carp
description: Cooking ingredient. A common type of fish that is easy to catch.

name: bass
description: Cooking ingredient. An aggressive fish that has thin, small teeth.

name: grass carp
description: Cooking ingredient. Fresh, delicious meat that is very suitable for cooking.

name: giant tiger prawn
description: Cooking ingredient. An especially large prawn found commonly in freshwater environments.

name: freshwater snail
description: Cooking ingredient. A snail that can be found in most places, lying lazily beneath the water's surface.

name: water weed
description: Cooking ingredient. A plant that grows underwater. It feels very wet.

name: frog
description: Cooking ingredient. A small animal with agitated cheeks. It makes a croaking sound.

name: watersnake
description: Cooking ingredient. A slippery Watersnake. If you don't firmly grasp it, it'll easily slip away from your hands.

name: sardine
description: A social fish of the sea that often swims in a group to scare off large predators. Can be used for cooking.

name: tuna
description: Cooking ingredient. Used in the cooking of high-grade fishes. Because of its high price, ordinary people can't often eat it.

name: squid
description: Cooking ingredient. Why does it seem that animals with tentacles are unexpectedly delicious when cooked?

name: pufferfish
description: Cooking ingredient. They become round when in danger. Chefs have to be careful of their poisonous spines.

name: hairtail
description: Cooking ingredient. It looks like a long, slender belt and swims quite elegantly in the water.

name: kelp
description: Cooking ingredient. Kelp that sways with the waves. It has high nutrition value.

name: algae
description: Cooking ingredient. Algae that lives on the seabed. It has a salty, fishy taste.

name: starlight snail
description: An island-style shell. If you hold it up to your ear, you can hear the ocean.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Enriched Elunium.

name: butterfly cowrie
description: This kind of scallop looks like a butterfly when it's opened, hence its name.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon III.

name: whitefeather cowrie
description: A sharp shell that is often used by seabed dwellers to make decorations.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Carnium III.

name: mystic mussel
description: A clam shell filled with mysterious power. Many mages favor them.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Bascyx III.

name: tube-eye
description: Its tail is like a slender whip with strong texture.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce STR Stone II and VIT Stone II.

name: emberfish
description: Lives in hot areas all year round. Its heat-resistant body makes it hard to cook.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Bascyx II.

name: glowfish
description: With a luminous ball on top of his head, it looks like a floating lamp in the water from a distance.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Enriched Oridecon.

name: arowana
description: Cooking ingredient. This large, colorful fish seems to be a favorite of Prontera's wealthy.

name: clearwater pearl
description: It's said that it was once a normal, unspectacular stone, but after a water aura coagulated around it, it turned into an extraordinary pearl. \nUsed as a smelting material to produce HD Bradium.

name: ghostfish
description: This glittering, translucent fish is actually a carnivorous creature, loving only rancid, rotten meat.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce HD Elunium.

name: soldierfish
description: Its scales are serrated and sharp.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce AGI Stone II and LUK Stone II.

name: vulcanfish
description: People in deserts regard this fish as a gift from the God of Fire.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon II.

name: devilfish
description: A ferocious, carnivorous fish with sharp teeth that glow with a cold light. It feeds on insects and small fish.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce HD Oridecon.

name: krill
description: Cooking ingredient. Emits a faint glow in the water at night.

name: giant shrimp
description: Cooking ingredient. A giant prawn that likes crawling along the water bed.

name: hardshell crab
description: A Vadon with an incredibly hard shell. It's very hard to handle without special processing.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Carnium II.

name: rainbow coral
description: Bright bits of coral that makes one think of rainbows in the sky.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce INT Stone II and DEX Stone II.

name: night pearl
description: A precious pearl that emits a fluorescent light in dark environments.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Enriched Bradium.

name: crayfish
description: Who would have guessed from its ingredients and plain appearance that this is actually a beloved delicacy in Midgard?

name: lotus seedpod
description: Cooking ingredient. An edible plant that grows in lakes.

name: shell
description: A common shell that can be found anywhere.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon I.

name: turquoise
description: A uniquely-colored stone.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Carnium I.

name: cobblestone
description: A small, smooth stone that's cool to the touch.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Bascyx I.

name: catfish
description: Cooking ingredient. A carnivorous fish whose meat is tender, with few bones and a rich taste.

name: river crab
description: Cooking ingredient. A delicious Vadon found commonly in freshwater environments.

name: conch
description: A spiral-shaped shell.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce STR Stone I and VIT Stone I.

name: white cloud fish
description: Groups of them often appear in mountain streams.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce AGI Stone I and LUK Stone I.

name: pure-water sturgeon
description: A valuable and extremely rare freshwater fish.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce INT Stone I and DEX Stone I.

name: silver carp
description: Cooking ingredient. A common freshwater fish that has a lively personality and is good at jumping.

name: pipefish
description: Cooking ingredient. A flexible fish with a pointed mouth and a slender body.

name: sheer marina
description: A small, cute, and dreamlike creature that feeds on rotten plants. It naturally gravitates toward the source of special odors.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Blessed Oridecon I.

name: sand-swallower
description: Lurking in the bottom of rivers, they purify their digestive system by huffing and puffing hard sand and stones.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Blessed Elunium I.

name: maple fish
description: Having a fiery-red color akin to maple leaves, it likes being near plants of colors similar to its own. Perhaps it's seeking a sense of security.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Blessed Bradium I.

name: carp
description: Cooking ingredient. A fish that is used for food, medicinal, and ornamental purposes.

name: gray-shell mussel
description: Cooking ingredient. Has a dusky-gray clam shell and is nothing special, but the meat inside is delicate and delicious.

name: trout
description: Cooking ingredient. A fish that has adapted for two homes, the trout has a freshwater form and marine form.

name: river eel
description: Cooking ingredient. It has a long, thin body and a cylindrical shape with sticky skin.

name: dusk fish
description: It gets its name from the gradual yellowing of its scales.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Blessed Oridecon II.

name: armored crab
description: Practically covered in a suit of armor, ordinary knives can't get at it.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Blessed Elunium II.

name: pupa sulcata
description: Its shell is covered in strange markings, giving it quite a mysterious look.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Blessed Bradium II.

name: green-backed fish
description: Cooking ingredient. A green-backed fish found in frozen waters. It's very healthy.

name: piranha
description: Cooking ingredient. A fish that has terrifying teeth. Some hobbyists catch it to use for aesthetic purposes.

name: yellow mantis shrimp
description: Cooking ingredient. A yellow mantis shrimp. As a food material, it is rare and difficult to handle.

name: blind loach
description: Cooking ingredient. It can be found in all kinds of shallow and muddy waters, and its meat is very delicious.

name: swordfish
description: It is named for its knife-like appearance and it violently attacks small living creatures.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon IV.

name: hunter fish
description: A ferocious fish with sharp teeth powerful enough to crush fishing hooks, though its body is weaker than one would expect.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Carnium IV.

name: crystal acanthodean
description: An ancient fish with spines as sharp as crystal.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Bascyx IV.

name: oyster
description: Cooking ingredient. Delicious shellfish.

name: sand shrimp
description: Cooking ingredient. A shrimp that lies in bodies of water close to shore.

name: deepwater frog
description: Cooking ingredient. A frog that prefers to live in deep bodies of water.

name: iron-eating tortoise
description: A tortoise with unusually sharp teeth that can devour metal.\nSmelting material. Used to synthesize STR Stone Ⅲ and VIT Stone Ⅲ.

name: fairy squid
description: A small squid with poor eyesight. Can only see brightly colored things.\nSmelting material. Used to synthesize AGI Stone III and LUK Stone III.

name: mantra fish
description: Very sensitive to magic. Earned its name from its tendency to approach anything with magic power.\nSmelting material. Used to synthesize INT Stone III and DEX Stone III.

name: great earth
description: A small, green piece of Great Earth imbued with the Earth attribute. Merchants can use it in production.

name: flame heart
description: A small, red piece of Flame Heart imbued with the Fire attribute. Merchants can use it in production.

name: rough wind
description: A small, yellow piece of Rough Wind imbued with the Wind attribute. Merchants can use it in production.

name: mystic frozen
description: A small, blue piece of Mystic Frozen imbued with the Water attribute. Merchants can use it in production.

name: red gemstone
description: An ore with magical powers. When using magic, it can replace the caster and negate the magic's counteractive power.

name: yellow gemstone
description: An ore with magical powers. When using magic, it can replace the caster and negate the magic's counteractive power.

name: lv.1 gold ore
description: A Lv.1 Gold Ore that contains gold. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Gold I.

name: lv.1 iron ore
description: A Lv.1 Iron Ore that contains iron. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Iron I.

name: lv.1 coal ore
description: A Lv.1 Coal Ore that contains coal. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nIt is a great smelting medium.

name: lv.1 silver ore
description: A Lv.1 Silver Ore that contains silver. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Silver I.

name: lv.1 impure jewelstone
description: A Lv.1 Impure Jewelstone that contains dark unknown substances.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce AGI Stone I, VIT Stone I, and DEX Stone I.

name: lv.1 rough bradium
description: A Lv.1 Rough Bradium that seems to contain certain magical powers.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Bradium.

name: lv.2 muspellium
description: A Lv.2 Muspellium that is very strong and highly resistant to flames, but extremely difficult to process.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Morroc Enchantment Stones.

name: lv.2 upgrading metal
description: A Lv.2 Upgrading Metal that feels cold to the touch.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon II, Carnium II, and Bascyx II.

name: lv.1 pure jewelstone
description: A Lv.1 Pure Jewelstone that is as untainted as glass.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce STR Stone I, INT Stone I, and LUK Stone I.

name: lv.3 muspellium
description: A Lv.3 Muspellium that is very strong and highly resistant to flames, but extremely difficult to process.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Izlude or Alberta Enchantment Stones.

name: lv.1 muspellium
description: A Lv.1 Muspellium that is very strong and highly resistant to flames, but extremely difficult to process.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Prontera Enchantment Stones.

name: lv.1 upgrading metal
description: A Lv.1 Upgrading Metal that feels cold to the touch.\nUsed as an upgrading material to upgrade weapons from levels 1 through 20, armor from levels 1 through 10, and accessories from levels 1 through 5.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon I, Carnium I, and Bascyx I.

name: lv.3 upgrading metal
description: A Lv.3 Upgrading Metal that feels cold to the touch.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon III, Carnium III, and Bascyx III.

name: lv.2 gold ore
description: A Lv.2 Gold Ore that contains gold. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Gold II.

name: lv.2 silver ore
description: A Lv.2 Silver Ore that contains silver. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Silver II.

name: lv.2 coal ore
description: A Lv.2 Coal Ore that contains coal. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nIt is a great smelting medium.

name: lv.2 iron ore
description: A Lv.2 Iron Ore that contains iron. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Iron II.

name: lv.2 pure jewelstone
description: A Lv.2 Pure Jewelstone that is as untainted as glass.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce STR Stone II, INT Stone II, and LUK Stone II.

name: lv.2 impure jewelstone
description: A Lv.2 Impure Jewelstone that contains dark unknown substances.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce AGI Stone II, VIT Stone II, and DEX Stone II.

name: lv.2 rough oridecon
description: A Lv.2 Rough Oridecon that is rare and hard to obtain.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Enriched Oridecon.

name: lv.2 rough bradium
description: A Lv.2 Rough Bradium that seems to contain certain magical powers.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Enriched Bradium.

name: lv.2 rough elunium
description: A Lv.2 Rough Elunium that contains Elunium metal. Further processing is required to reveal its true value.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Enriched Elunium.

name: lv.1 blessed ore
description: A Lv.1 Blessed Ore that is imbued with protective power.\nUsed as smelting material to produce Blessed Oridecon I, Blessed Elunium I, and Blessed Bradium I.

name: lv.4 muspellium
description: A Lv.4 Muspellium that is very strong and highly resistant to flames, but extremely difficult to process.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Payon and Geffen Enchantment Stones.

name: lv.4 upgrading metal
description: A Lv.4 Upgrading Metal that feels cold to the touch.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce Phracon IV, Carnium IV, and Bascyx IV.

name: lv.3 rough oridecon
description: A Lv.3 Rough Oridecon that is rare and hard to obtain.\nUsed as a smelting material to produce HD Oridecon.

name: savage bebe meat

name: livestock gore
description: Blood taken from some kind of animal, it has a fishy smell. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

description: Nutritious bones have no other shortcomings except being a little hard. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: bitter herb
description: This bitter grass becomes sweet when chewed. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: goldflower nectar
description: Golden sticky honey that emits a sweet fragrance. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: fresh cheese
description: No mouse can ever resist cheese, at least not Tarou. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Tarou to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.1 Taming.

name: deadly noxious herb
description: A delicate poisonous grass, it's extremely dangerous. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: juicy grape
description: Fresh and juicy grapevine, high in sugar content. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: morning dew
description: Transparent dew still rolls on the leaves. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: baked sweet potato

name: tropical banana
description: Premium quality banana grown in the tropics. Yoyo finds it to be very tasty. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Yoyo to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.2 Taming.

name: discarded coin
description: Dull ancient coins that have value as collectors items. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: worn bronze armor
description: Partially worn copper armor, still very awe-inspiring if you look closely. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: monster juice
description: A drink made of bird's blood. Hunter Fly finds it to be very tasty. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Hunter Fly to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.2 Taming.

name: ghost coffin
description: A coffin made of oak wood. Whisper really likes it. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Whisper to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.3 Taming.

name: juicy cactus
description: The juiciest cactus in the desert. Muka finds it to be very tasty. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Muka to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.3 Taming.

name: fatty chubby earthworm
description: A healthy and chubby Hode. Pecopeco finds it to be very tasty. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Pecopeco to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.3 Taming.

name: deadly venom
description: Deadly venom secreted and loved by Anacondaqs, it's their favorite item. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Anacondaq to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.3 Taming.

name: thick pelt
description: A thick pelt that can be used to keep warm. Sasquatch really likes it. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Sasquatch to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.3 Taming.

name: poisonous scorpion stinger
description: The tail of a scorpion that doesn't look like a filling food, but Side Winder finds it to be very tasty. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Side Winder to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.3 Taming.

name: magical lithography
description: A magical stone slab. The materials used and inscription cannot be dated. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: small wok
description: A superior quality small wok obtained from an elite chef. Magnolia really likes it. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Magnolia to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.3 Taming.

name: monster moss
description: Moss that drinks morning dew. Marina finds it to be very tasty. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Marina to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.4 Taming.

name: mithril arrow
description: An arrow made of Mithril. Archer Skeleton really likes it. Learn Pet Taming and use it on an Archer Skeleton to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.4 Taming.

name: armlet of obedience
description: It's said this is a relic of a master animal tamer. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: dark ink
description: Ink darker than night, anything stained by it is hard to wash off. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: silvery shell
description: Expensive shells, a good choice for making jewelry. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: singing flower

name: no recipient

name: her heart

name: old broom
description: An old magic broom, it has other uses aside from sweeping. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: broken egg shell
description: Broken egg shards, the creature inside has long gone. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: flail-wielding goblin ring

name: sweet milk
description: Magic milk with a swet, smooth taste. Can be used for pet capture and interaction (Each capture will consume 6 of this capture item).

name: heavy cuffs
description: Cuffs made of lead. Mace-wielding Kobold really likes it. Learn Pet Taming and use it on a Mace-wielding Kobold to tame it (this pet taming item is consumed on every attempt). Requires Lv.5 Taming.

name: orc trophy

name: fragrant cassia twig
description: Gift item. Autumn's osmanthus branches and leaves. With their fresh, pleasant fragrance, they are most suitable for pairing with wine and creating a romantic atmosphere.

name: old weapon
description: Gift item. A weapon with a style that seems to precede Ragnarok. It is full of history and may or may not have a soul attached to it.

name: scarlet wine
description: Gift item. Wine made from a mysterious fruit. It has a bright, blood-red color and an incredibly complex taste. It seems it would be perfect for a night of storytelling.

name: lost gold bracelet
description: Gift item. A somewhat old-looking bracelet made of pure gold and covered in gorgeous gemstones. It's unknown who left it behind.

name: maple sugar cake
description: Gift item. A maple-flavored cake that seems to be some chef's secret recipe. It tastes like pure bliss.

name: doll pendant
description: Gift item. A cute plush doll pendant. People can't help but smile at its cute expression. It's a healing gift that can bring happiness.

name: luminous scale
description: Gift item. Blue scales that glitter in the night. They seem to have come from some deep-sea fish.

name: coral crystal
description: Gift item. A white coral crystal from the seabed. It's said to emit a mysterious blue glow under the moonlight.

name: lost treasure
description: Gift item. A treasure chest from an unknown ancient shipwreck, overgrown with seaweed. Its value is unknown.

name: lakebed pearl
description: Gift item. High-quality pearls scattered at the bottom of the lake. They seem to have come not from natural clam shells, but from a treasure chest overturned by some nobles.

name: topaz
description: Gift item. A hard and warm yellow gemstone that becomes warm due to human body temperature. It's a kind of valuable decorative ore.

name: obsidian
description: Gift item. Ore formed by the sudden cooling of lava flowing out of a volcano. It is said the person who possesses it will never cry again. This crystal-clear black gem is also an indispensable accessory for fashionable people.

name: amethyst
description: Gift item. A mysterious gemstone that possesses a strong divination power. It is especially expensive due to its beautiful appearance and seems to be a must-have for those interested in the occult.

name: cosmic stone
description: Gift item. A crystalline ore with a faint green luster. It is as hard as steel, and it is commonly used for decorative purposes due to its excellent brilliance.

name: refreshing dew
description: Gift item. The dew of dawn taken from the leaves of plants deep in the forest. It is sweet, cool, and reminiscent of the nighttime summer breeze.

name: golden feather
description: Gift item. A golden feather, with a faint luster of dark gold. It seems to come from some kind of legendary sacred bird, but no one has seen what it actually looks like.

name: magic waste
description: Gift item. A decaying plant that exudes hidden magic power. Due to its decay, it is impossible to distinguish what it once was. It is often used to provide nutrients for new plants.

name: leaf bookmark
description: Gift item. These delicate green leaves are often used as bookmarks because they are so cute and light.

name: sad clown music box
description: \"Flessi\" is carved in the bottom of this antique music box, while the top has a sad clown wearing an over-the-top wig on it. Seemingly worn down over time, the paint is chipping off somewhat, and the brass winding mechanism has begun to rust a bit, making it no longer able to be wound up. Perhaps the only way you'll be able to understand the story behind it is by asking the music box's owner, Flessi. Once used, your fate will be mysteriously bound to Flessi's.

name: crystal heart
description: The continent of Midgard is home to the most precious of crystals. Legend states that it was formed before the destruction of Yggdrasil and was soaked in the power of its roots. It is perfectly clear and free of impurities, and it emits a colorful glow beneath the sunlight. The crystal merchant Sinclair is rumored to be searching everywhere for it. Once used, your fate will be mysteriously bound to Sinclair's.

name: oliver wolf eyeball
description: This translucent, clever-looking eye belonging to the Wolf King looks like a blue gem without careful inspection. Among Desert Wolf packs, whenever a Wolf King dies, the other wolves in their pack will remove the Wolf King's eyeball and pass it down as a vessel of strength. It's said to be a necessary material for crafting Oliver Wolf Headgear, and recently, Geffen's headgear merchant Ingael has issued a bounty in an attempt to get it. Once used, your fate will be mysteriously bound to Ingael's.

name: super kart figure
description: The figure of a race car from another world. It is said that in this other world, a race car is a super mount with speed comparable to using a Fly Wing.\nIt is rumored to be a beloved item of an adventurer from another world who is popular in Prontera. Give this to this adventurer to increase your Favor with him.

name: magnificent sports car figure
description: The figure of a race car from another world. Its bright green body gives it a feeling of boundless energy that makes one unable to look away.\nIt is rumored to be a beloved item of an adventurer from another world who is popular in Prontera. Give this to this adventurer to increase your Favor with him

name: f1 race car figure
description: The figure of a race car from another world. The exquisite appearance seems to hint that this race car from another world is a remarkable invention.\nIt is rumored to be a beloved item of an adventurer from another world who is popular in Prontera. Give this adventurer to increase your Favor with him

name: meteor shard
description: Part of a meteorite found in Sograt Desert. Emitting a faint reddish glow, it seems to contain a mysterious power. However, no one can say exactly what purpose it may serve. Rumor has it that Hollgrehenn, the greatest blacksmith in Prontera, is collecting meteorite fragments just like this one.

description: A tattered page from ancient tome. A glimmer of magic shines through the words.\nFishing bait. Used for fishing in Glast Heim.

name: imperial cooking kit
description: Cooking kit reserved for the royals.\nUsed to cook Lv.9 food items.

name: premium white medicine kit
description: A kit containing Advanced White Potions. Use it to obtain 100 Advanced White Potions.

name: premium pvp white medicine kit
description: A kit containing Advanced White Potions (PVP). Use it to obtain 100 Advanced White Potions (PVP).

name: silver bream
description: Cooking ingredient. Fresh sea bream that can be grilled for a simple yet tasty dish.

name: salt crab
description: Cooking ingredient. A type of crab that crystallizes salt and spreads it across the surface of its body.

name: lizard eel
description: Resembles both a lizard and an eel. Feeds on nutritious worms.\nSmelting material. Used to synthesize High Density Elunium.

name: veiled shark
description: A fish that's good at concealing itself. Often hides beneath fine sand to lie in wait for scented prey.\nSmelting material. Used to synthesize High Density Oridecon.

name: magnetic crystal
description: Ore found on the sea floor. Has a natural magnetic force and can attach itself to metal.\nSmelting material. Used to synthesize High Density Bradium.

name: houndstooth sturgeon
description: A marine sturgeon with crisscrossing teeth. It sometimes uses debris or wood chips to sharpen its teeth.\nSmelting Material used to synthesize Phracon V.

name: sugar marina
description: A large marina that is attracted to food with sugar.\nSmelting Material used to synthesize Carnium V.

name: crow crab
description: A group of scavenging crabs, often seen as ominous things.\nSmelting Material used to synthesize Bascyx V.

name: rust striped fish
description: A fish with a dark brown pattern that looks like rust spots from afar.\nSmelting Material used to synthesize Protected Oridecon III.

name: incense fish
description: Sensitive to scented bait, hence the name.\nSmelting Material used to synthesize Protected Elunium III.

name: sharp kiss fish
description: A small fish with a pointed mouth.\nSmelting Material used to synthesize Protected Bradium III.

name: palette surgeonfish
description: Surgeonfish with a royal blue and bright yellow body. It seems to offer a pretty good taste too?

name: box crab
description: Be careful not to hurt your toes by what may look like steamed buns on the beach! These box crabs are Comodo's signature creatures.

name: striped beakfish
description: Precious species that are often caught because they are curious about everything.

name: 鬼鮟鱇
description: 形貌奇丑的古老鱼种，发光的触角是它捕食的诱饵。

name: 巨针海胆
description: 长满巨刺的海胆，即使被捉到也无从下口。

name: 魔骷鱼
description: 一点肉都没有的鱼类，或许可以煲出美味的鱼汤。

name: 角鳝
description: 头部生有尖角的细鳞鱼，在漆黑的洞穴中生活。

name: 泥刺螺
description: 栖息在水底淤泥的硬壳螺，壳上带有弯曲的刺状物。

name: 巨壳龟
description: 咬合力极强的外来物种，有一定攻击性。

name: 甲虫内脏
description: 外形扭曲的腥臭饵料，上面还有未干的甲虫体液。\n鱼饵，可在汶巴拉的钓鱼点使用。

name: 毛绒线团
description: 用生物纤维织成的毛线团，遇水会膨胀。\n鱼饵，可在汶巴拉的钓鱼点使用。

name: 腐烂肉块
description: 从病变的生物尸体上割下，勉强保留“肉”的形状。\n鱼饵，可在汶巴拉的钓鱼点使用。

name: strelitzia
description: Cooking ingredient shaped like a crane. The flower is a symbol of longing for a lover, regardless of where or when.

name: udumbara
description: Cooking ingredient. This flower is very rare and extremely difficult to come across, but somehow it blooms like a weed somewhere on Comodo.

name: evening primrose
description: Cooking ingredient. It can well adapt to the sandy environment of Comodo and is a very nutritious plant.

name: hyacinth
description: A violet flower that is highly ornamental. It has a variety of usage and is easy to grow.\nSmelting material. It can be used to synthesize Enchantment Stones of Comodo.

name: speedwell
description: A flower that blooms on grass branches that look like wolf tails, as if a sword that slashes monsters.\nSmelting material. It can be used to synthesize Enchantment Stones of Comodo.

name: flame iris
description: The Comodo residents describe it as a flame that leaped and danced in the wind.\nSmelting material. It can be used to synthesize Enchantment Stones of Comodo.

name: 灰色药草
description: 拥有特殊香气且能让人精神饱满的灰色药草。

name: uhd oridecon
description: A mysterious metal known as Oridecon. It is the hardest matter ever found.\nUsed as a material to refine weapons from levels 13 through 15.

name: uhd elunium
description: A very light, non-toxic metal.\nUsed as a material to refine armor from levels 13 through 15.

name: uhd bradium
description: One of the hardest metals found in the Ash Vacuum, difficult to temper because of its high density.\nUsed as a material to refine accessories from levels 13 through 15.

name: blessed oridecon ⅱi
description: A grade I blessed stone that seems to contain a protective power specially for weapons.\nUsed as a material to protect weapons from levels 13 through 15 from damage upon refinement failure.

name: weapon protection stone i
description: A grade I protection stone imbued with power that can be used in weapon refinement from levels 5 through 8.\nThe refinement will not be downgraded after using the protection stone. However, due to the large amount of magical power in the stone, the weapon being protected will be affected by energy backlash during refinement. The backlash significantly reduces the chance of upgrading the weapon refinement, and significantly increase the chance of damage.\nAfter the refinement is used, the item will be consumed and the effect will be active whenever the refinement is done at levels 5 through 8. When using both equipment protection and blessed equipment stones, the number of blessed equipment stones consumed will be doubled.

description: Enchantment material. Used to grant weapons Aldebaran's Dark Stillness enchantment.

name: solar enchantment stone

description: Enchantment material. Used to grant accessories Aldebaran's Starlight enchantment.

description: Enchantment material. Use to grant weapons Comodo's [Violet] enchantment.

name: charcoal powder
description: Cooking ingredient. This ashy powder is a good combustion agent.

name: magic spice
description: Cooking ingredient. Spice developed with the aid of magic. Has a distinct fragrance.

name: steel thorn
description: Cooking ingredient. A slender metal thorn. Looks quite fragile.

name: nut

description: Cooking ingredient. A very tough branch that's hard to break.

name: hard flour
description: Cooking ingredient. Flour that is a little damp.

name: roasted kebab ⅰ
description: A plain kebab feeding countless Comodo residences. Eat it to gain Stun RES +23%, and Blind RES +23% for 30 minutes.

name: special seafood fried rice i
description: A main dish cooked with various Kokomo seafood and flavoring spices. Eat it to gain Freeze RES +23%, and Curse RES +23% for 30 minutes.

name: seashore salad i
description: Delicious salad with a touch of the sea. A single bite is totally addictive. Eat it to gain Immobilization RES +23%, and Poison RES +23% for 30 minutes.

name: snapper wrapping meat i
description: Tenderloin wrapped with the finest snapper skin, and then roasted to enhance the aroma and flavor. With the rich taste and aroma, it is famous on Comodo. Eat it to gain Petrify RES +23%, and Bleed RES +23% for 30 minutes.

name: spicy fried crab i
description: Hot, and brings happiness. Come and feel how the tender flesh of crabs dance on your tongue. Eat it to gain Sleep RES +23%, and Armor Breakage RES +23% for 30 minutes.

name: stone-roasted snapper i
description: Cooked with special spices and the most natural method, the flavor is reserved as much as possible. Eat it to gain Silence RES +23%, and Weapon Breakage RES +23% for 30 minutes.

name: golden jar cookies
description:
Eat it to obtain 1-hour Golden Jar Cookies Blessing.
Legend has it that after a bond is created between you and someone who has eaten Silver Jar Cookies when you are near them, both of you will be rewarded with a Paper Crane and 12-hour Cupid’s Blessing when you make a Heart Emote within a short period of time.
Note: The effect may be upgraded when you obtain Cupid’s Blessing more than once!
<color=#FF0000>[Will be taken back after the event ends. Come eat it within the event!]</color>

name: silver jar cookies
description:
Eat it to obtain 1-hour Silver Jar Cookies Blessing.
Legend has it that after a bond is created between you and someone who has eaten Gold Jar Cookies when you are near them, both of you will be rewarded with a Paper Crane and 12-hour Cupid’s Blessing when you make a Heart Emote within a short period of time.
Note: The effect may be upgraded when you obtain Cupid’s Blessing more than once!
<color=#FF0000>[Will be taken back after the event ends. Come eat it within the event!]</color>

name: hip-hop chain
description: An item used to unlock the Skeleton Worker pet's transmorg, Hip-hop Chain. A popular accessory among miners that displays their obsession with precious metals.

name: miner backpack
description: An item used to unlock the Giearth pet's transmorg, Miner Backpack. Giearth can discern who the owner is by the details so you will never take the wrong backpack by mistake.

name: gold band
description: An item used to unlock the Yoyo pet's transmorg, Gold Band. Every owner and Yoyo can completely prove their closeness, and they convey a little zen.

name: deviruchi wing
description: An item used to unlock the Phreeoni pet's transmorg, Deviruchi Wing. Phreeoni move lighter after wearing them, which may just be a psychological effect.

name: diving helmet
description: An item used to unlock the Baby Desert Wolf pet's transmorg, Diving Helmet. The diving helmet is snow white, so one day it will be able to play in the water, right?

name: firetooth helmet
description: An item used to unlock the Desert Wolf pet's transmorg, Desert Wolf. The Desert Wolf lives on hot sand, so it's most suitable for the helmet to be made of steel.

name: bio mask
description: An item used to unlock the Drainliar pet's transmorg, Bio Mask. A mask that is used to deal with Drainliar that are not completely domesticated yet. It has gradually become fashionable.

name: wind-shield glasses
description: An item used to unlock the Familiar pet's transmorg, Wind-shield Glasses. It does not usually rely on its sense of sight, but eyes should still be protect... probably.

name: colorful glasses
description: An item used to unlock the Rocker pet's transmorg, Colorful Glasses. Fans of rock think different and prefer eye-catching and fancy designs.

name: gentleman glasses
description: An item used to unlock the Grasshopper pet's transmorg, Gentleman Glasses. Don't let them get anywhere near the old books. Who knows if their hunger is for knowledge or for food.

name: rose wreath
description: An item used to unlock the Eclipse pet's transmorg, Rose Wreath. It's not recommended to buy expensive rabbit headgear because it's often disposable.

name: butterfly bow
description: An item used to unlock the Lunatic pet's transmorg, Butterfly Bow. Some rabbits might go semi-permanently mad from discomfort after wearing it. Quite normal.

name: adventure backpack
description: An item used to unlock the Mastering pet's transmorg, Adventure Backpack. Maybe years have passed but King Poring's dreams of adventure from when he was young has not faded at all.

name: poring backpack
description: An item used to unlock the Poring pet's transmorg, Poring Backpack. It's said that a Poring's backpack contains a part of itself to save its life in case of danger...

name: butterfly mask
description: An item used to unlock the Hornet pet's transmorg, Butterfly Mask. A ball is a necessity for the life of soldier bees, and also a battlefield for fashion.

name: alchemy mask
description: An item used to unlock the Mistress pet's transmorg, Alchemy Mask. What exactly does the queen bee's compound eyes see through lenses filled with magic?

name: bamboo dragonfly
description: An item used to unlock the Dustiness pet's transmorg, Bamboo Dragonfly. A small bamboo dragonfly designed just for Dustiness. It can't fly and doesn't need to.

name: star crown
description: An item used to unlock the Dragon Fly pet's transmorg, Star Crown. The length can be adjusted to fit, and it's suitable for dragon flies of all ages and sizes.

name: swimming goggles
description: An item used to unlock the Roda Frog pet's transmorg, Swimming Goggles. They say there's a trend among the Roda Frog s that \"practicality is beauty.\"

name: diving goggles
description: An item used to unlock the Frog King pet's transmorg, Diving Goggles. Why do some species need special tools to move underwater?

name: illuminated unicorn
description: An item used to unlock the Whisper pet's transmorg, Illuminated Unicorn. Hard objects can make light, floaty ghosts seem real.

name: inferno horn
description: An item used to unlock the Ghostring pet's transmorg, Inferno Horn. The Ghostring is very satisfied with this—finally! It can dress up as a real devil!

name: bell of fortune
description: An item used to unlock the Side Winder pet's transmorg, Bell of Fortune. The Anacondaq will beat time with bells, and it might lead the snakes in a rap.

name: star halo
description: An item used to unlock the Snake pet's transmorg, Star Halo. To balance the nastiness of the side winder's reputation. However, it seems to scare even more people away.

name: wanderer’s scarf
description: An item used to unlock the Zombie pet's transmorg, Wanderer’s Scarf. The burial did not completely take away the rotting bodies, but their upper garments.

name: zealot mask
description: An item used to unlock the Ghoul pet's transmorg, Zealot Mask. This mask will show off the Ghoul's teeth and handsome side.

name: butterfly bell
description: An item used to unlock the Moonlight Flower pet's transmorg, Butterfly Bell. This accessory harmonizes with the fur, and also symbolizes the imprint of civilization.

name: midnight horong
description: An item used to unlock the Myst pet's transmorg, Midnight Horong. Raising Myst requires a certain amount of guts, so making accessories for them is even more...

name: pulse headset
description: An item used to unlock the Sasquatch pet's transmorg, Pulse Headset. They make Sasquatch look more human-like, because the headphones aren't even on their ears...

name: tri-color wig
description: An item used to unlock the Golem pet's transmorg, Tri-color Wig. These warm stone friends are finally showing the tri-color wig some attention.

name: gorgeous feather
description: Soft fur obtained from Lunatic. It is an excellent crafting material for headgears.

name: dancing grass
description: A magical herb that radiates rainbow-colored rays.

name: halo replica blueprint
description: A blueprint necessary to craft Angeling's Halo replica.

name: lucky clover

name: angeling's halo
description: The valkyries bestowed this halo containing their divine power upon Angeling.

name: vital flower

name: rose ring

name: petal rain
description: A romantic item specially made by the Magic Guild. Produces the romantic effect of petals falling from the sky after use, covering guests in a floral shower. Particularly suitable for weddings.

name: dreamy champagne
description: The top champagne from the finest winery in Midgard, it fizzes with luxuriant bubbles and a charming aroma when opened. Spraying its foam creates extraordinary momentum before any banquet. A must for wedding celebrations and other occasions.

name: hearts entwined
description: A romantic item specially made by the Magic Guild. Produces heart-shaped bubbles and colorful twinkling stars after use, symbolizing the beauty of romance. Especially suitable for creating a romantic atmosphere at weddings and other occasions.

name: perfect match (left)
description: A romantic item specially made by the Magic Guild. The left wing of Cupid. A solitary Cupid wing appears behind the user, allowing them to float through the air and land directly in the spotlight. If two people use the left and right wings together, the effect will be even more magnificent.

name: perfect match (right)
description: A romantic item specially made by the Magic Guild. The right wing of Cupid. A solitary Cupid wing appears behind the user, allowing them to float through the air and land directly in the spotlight. If two people use the left and right wings together, the effect will be even more magnificent.

name: cupid descends
description: A romantic item specially made by the Magic Guild. Calls upon Cupid to fire a golden arrow of love at whoever uses it. Especially suitable for sweet occasions, such as weddings.

name: wedding invitation (family and friends)
description: Proof for attending your friend's wedding as a member of their Family and Friends group. Witness their moment of happiness.

name: wedding invitation (guest)
description: Proof for attending your friend's wedding as a member of their Guest group. Witness their moment of happiness.

name: jimmy lin witness voucher
description: Proof of obtaining Jimmy Lin's favor. Owning this item allow you to select Jimmy Lin as your wedding witness in the Couple Series.

name: marvelous spirit
description: Represents the honest love between you and your partner. Used to level up Couple Skills.

name: freyja's collection i
description: A mysterious crystal that exudes an air of love. Use to obtain 5 Couple EXP.

name: freyja's collection ii
description: A mysterious crystal that exudes an overwhelming air of love. Use to obtain 10 Couple EXP.

name: normal dice
description: Use to roll the dice for a random number. You will move forward a number of steps corresponding to the dice roll. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: remote control dice
description: Use to control the dice to roll a number. You will move forward a number of steps corresponding to the dice roll. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: angel dice
description: Use to roll the dice for one of the following random numbers: 4, 5, or 6. You will move forward a number of steps corresponding to the dice roll. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: demon dice
description: Use to roll the dice for one of the following random numbers: 1, 2, or 3. You will move forward a number of steps corresponding to the dice roll. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: normalization dice
description: Use to roll the dice for 1. You will move forward a number of steps corresponding to the dice roll. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: lucky dice
description: Use to roll the dice for 6. You will move forward a number of steps corresponding to the dice roll. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: starry dice
description: Use to roll the dice for a random number. You will obtain a number of Starshine Coins corresponding to the dice roll. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: blind box dice
description: Use to roll the dice for a random number. You will obtain a number of dice corresponding to the dice roll. These dice will not be Normal Dice or Blind Box Dice. (Can only be used in Wonderland.)

name: random dice gift box
description:
Grants one of the following items:
2 Angel Dice,

1 Normalization Dice,
1 Lucky Dice,
1 Remote Control Dice,
